            if 'Accessories' in r.get('网站分类',''):
                paras=[f"{r['产品名称（英文）']} is a configuration accessory for electronic titration or dispensing systems.","It is listed independently so each holder, adapter, probe, printer, software module, or liquid-path accessory can be ordered, replaced, and checked for compatibility without relying on the main instrument record.","The function and reference information from the source material are retained in the specification table for traceable configuration and after-sales support."]
